		<a href="https://raw.github.com/toepoke/Fluqi/master/Fluqi.Tests/Accordion/AccordionTests-Core.cs">Accordion_Can_Override_Container_HTML_And_Header_HTML_And_Content_HTML_Tags</a>
		test for an illustration.
		</li>
	</ul>

